AddressInfo.Title: Woodburn Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From I-5 N:  Take exit 271 for OR-214 toward Woodburn;  Turn left onto OR-214/OR-219 N/Newberg Hwy;  Turn right onto N Arney Rd;  Turn right to stay on N Arney Rd;  Take the 1st left in to the parking lot;  Take the second right, in front of Elmer’s;  Drive to the end of the parking lot;  Supercharger will be on the left.  /  From I-5S:  Take exit 271 for OR-214 toward Woodburn/Silverton;  Turn right onto OR-219 N;  Take the 1st right onto N Arney Rd;  Turn right to stay on N Arney Rd;  Take the 1st left in to the parking lot; Take the second right, in front of Elmer’s;  Drive to the end of the parking lot;  Supercharger will be on the left.
